title.rendered: Terumo Sharps Container Bin Screw Lid 1.4L

content.rendered: Terumo Sharps Containers are used for discarding contaminated sharps waste including used hypodermic needles, syringes, scalpels, lancets and devices used in medical, surgical and home heathcare environments. Terumo Sharps Containers Design Benefits: The containers are certified to: Disposable Container Standard AS/NZS AS 4031:1992, standards OSHA USA requirements and British Standard 7320 and display high puncture-resistance (exceeds all Standards, eliminates penetration and Sharps Injury Risk
